id: pm-vi2v
title: Add governance normalize command with dry-run and apply modes
description: Implement a first-class pm command that detects low-signal metadata patterns and optionally applies deterministic normalization updates with auditable mutation plans.
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 1
tags[4]: automation,governance,normalization,pm-cli
created_at: "2026-04-04T21:55:02.727Z"
